### Which @angular/* package(s) are the source of the bug?

core

### Is this a regression?

No

### Description

Input:
```
<ng-template
  [ngIf]="mode === 'foo'"
  [ngIfThen]="foo"
  [ngIfElse]="bar"
></ng-template>

<ng-template #foo>
  Foo
</ng-template>

<ng-template #bar>
  Bar
</ng-template>

```

Output:
```
@if (mode === 'foo') {
  <ng-template
    [ngIfThen]="foo"
    [ngIfElse]="bar"
  ></ng-template>
} @else {
  Bar
}
<ng-template #foo>
  Foo
</ng-template>
<ng-template #bar>
  Bar
</ng-template>
```

Expected output:

```
@if (mode === 'foo') {
  Foo
} @else {
  Bar
}
```

This is a similar issue to https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/53251

